===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fro}} {{term|entretenir|lang=fro}} < {{term|entre||among|lang=fro}} + {{term|tenir||to hold|lang=fro}} < {{etyl|la}} {{term|inter|lang=la}} + {{term|teneo|teneō|hold, keep|lang=la}}.

